<section class="brand--department-of-health brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="featured-documents">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Featured</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="gem-c-image-card gem-c-image-card--large brand--department-of-health">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Dame Fiona Caldicott" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69495/s712_sep172015.JPG"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-03-11">11 March 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Press release</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/dame-fiona-caldicott-appointed-as-the-first-statutory-national-data-guardian-for-health-and-social-care">Dame Fiona Caldicott appointed as the first statutory National Data Guardian for Health and Social Care</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Secretary of State for Health and Social Care has invited Dame Fiona Caldicott to be the first holder of the statutory office of National Data Guardian for Health and Social Care.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--department-of-health">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Citizens' jury deliberating" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/64953/s465_citizenjury2.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-08-13">13 August 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Speech</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/speeches/talking-with-citizens-about-expectations-for-data-sharing-and-privacy">Talking with citizens about expectations for data sharing and privacy</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>We asked a citizen’s jury to tell us what uses of confidential patient information it’s reasonable to expect. Today we publish the jury’s findings and reflect on what they told us.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--department-of-health">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="National Data Guardian consultation on priorities" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69696/s465_NDG_consultation.jpeg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-18">18 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Closed consultation</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/consultations/national-data-guardian-a-consultation-on-priorities">National Data Guardian: a consultation on priorities</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>We want to hear views on the key priorities for the National Data Guardian for Health and Social Care, as the role moves to a new phase.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

